# ==============================================================================
# INPO Empirical Benchmarking Suite
# Description: Generates IEEE-formatted quantitative figures for Section III:
# 1. Denoising Benchmark (PSNR/SSIM vs Noise Density)
# 2. Entropy Reduction (Compression Bar Chart)
# 3. Terminal Attractor Convergence (Phase Plot for BIBO Stability)
